-- GDF Suez, China National Nuclear Sign Fuel Production Agreement, Echo Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-07T04:40:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/gdf-suez-china-national-nuclear-sign-fuel-production-agreement-echo-says.html
GDF Suez SA has signed an accord with
China National Nuclear Corp. to help it build a pilot Mox
nuclear-fuel factory in China, Les Echos reported, without
citing anyone.  GDF aims to compete with Areva SA in the Mox market in
China, according to the newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
 dwhitehouse1@bloomberg.net  